| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3760 — Recovery Inhibition (arcusmedia)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8c6656de-7001-5d98-a826-1e4333ae03a0"
